rows.label: xs02050100_MSG0002
rows.name: Well now, look what the cat dragged in...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02050100_MSG0003
rows.name:
Sorry we missed you last time—
we could have come to meet you at HQ, you know.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02050100_MSG0005
rows.name: And we know how much I enjoy being told what to do.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02050100_MSG0006
rows.name:
Anyway, I hear you tangled with a tyrant
WAY out of your league. On a training mission, no less.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02050100_MSG0007
rows.name: That was reckless. And goddamn magnificent.[ST:wait ]
